          "description": "I went back to LIV Dentistry for a second procedure, and I can say with total confidence that this practice is remarkably consistent. The values I experienced the first time\u2014genuine care and incredible attention to patient needs\u2014were front and center once again.\n\nI can\u2019t say enough about Dr. Mehrzadi and the wonderful staff. They laid out a treatment plan that I feel 100% confident in, especially because they were so mindful of my budgetary needs. To the office staff and the dental specialists (Special shoutout to Lordlyn!!!): thank you for making me feel like a part of the LIV Dentistry Family.\n\nMost importantly, they have truly eased my dental anxieties. The professionalism and care I\u2019ve experienced here have completely changed how I feel about going to the dentist. If you want to feel seen, heard, and cared for, this is the place to be!",
