          "description": "This place is phenomenal. Yaharia, Cece, the girls and Dr. Mehrzahi are angels from God. I came all the way from Westchester County and found this place who not accepted my insurance, but was filled with smiles and patience the entire time I was in tears due to so much pain.\n\nI\u2019m so utterly grateful for this team and please visit them if you need any dental work. I will travel an hour away all over again for their expertise. Thank you for existing and being soooo helpful when people feel their lowest. God bless. See you soon LIV Dentistry.",
